---
---
<!-- Hero Section - Clean phase overview -->
<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20" id="hero-section">
	<div class="text-center mb-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
			Engineering the Web's <span class="text-[var(--accent-cyan)] drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(34,211,238,0.3)]">First Layer</span>
		</h1>

		<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[var(--text-body)] mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
			Maryland-based computer systems design practice specializing in <strong class="text-[var(--text-header)]">Digital Transformation</strong> and <strong class="text-[var(--text-header)]">Custom Systems Design</strong>.
			Fast, secure, and built for growth.
		</p>

		<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-stretch sm:items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-16">
			<a href="/contact" class="bg-[var(--accent)] text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-[var(--accent-hover)] transition-colors duration-200 min-h-[48px] flex items-center justify-center">
				Start Your Project
			</a>
			<a href="/work" class="bg-[var(--bg-page)] text-[var(--text-header)] border border-[var(--stroke)] px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-[var(--bg-muted)] transition-colors duration-200 min-h-[48px] flex items-center justify-center">
				See Our Work
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Phase cards -->
	<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
		<div class="bg-[var(--bg-card)] border border-[var(--stroke)] rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6">
			<span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 1</span>
			<h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-header)] mt-1 mb-2">$0 Credited Consultation</h3>
			<p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-body)] leading-relaxed">
				Initial consultation fees are credited toward your final project cost. Requirements analysis and project specifications.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="bg-[var(--bg-card)] border border-[var(--stroke)] rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6">
			<span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 2</span>
			<h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-header)] mt-1 mb-2">Fixed-Price MVP</h3>
			<p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-body)] leading-relaxed">
				Complete MVPs with clear deliverables, timelines, and budgets. Three revision rounds included.
			</p>
			<p class="text-xs text-[var(--accent)] font-medium mt-3">60-Day Post-Launch Support Included</p>
		</div>

		<div class="bg-[var(--bg-card)] border border-[var(--stroke)] rounded-lg p-5 sm:p-6">
			<span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--text-muted)] uppercase tracking-wider">Phase 3</span>
			<h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--text-header)] mt-1 mb-2">Hourly Production Scaling</h3>
			<p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-body)] leading-relaxed">
				Ongoing maintenance, feature enhancements, and iterative development beyond MVP scope.
			</p>
			<p class="text-xs text-[var(--accent)] font-medium mt-3">60-Day Support + Optional Retainers</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
